<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Pooja Booking Cancelled</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #ffebee; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .details { background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Pooja Booking Cancelled</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Respected Pandit Ji,</p>
            
            <p>The following booking assigned to you has been cancelled by the devotee:</p>
            
            <div class="details">
                <h3>Booking Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> <%= bookingId %></p>
                <p><strong>Pooja:</strong> <%= poojaName %></p>
                <p><strong>Devotee Name:</strong> <%= userName %></p>
                <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <%= userPhone %></p>
                <p><strong>Cancellation Time:</strong> <%= cancellationTime %></p>
            </div>
            
            <p>This booking has been removed from your schedule. If you have any questions, please contact the Vaidic Parampara support team.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Vaidic Parampara. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>